---
description: Use expo-paystack for Paystack payments in Expo apps
globs: **/*.tsx, **/*.ts
---

When integrating Paystack payments in an Expo app:
- Use expo-paystack, not react-native-paystack-webview
- Always wrap root with PaystackProvider
- Amount is in smallest currency unit (kobo for NGN)
- Use usePaystack() hook and initializePayment()
- Verify transactions server-side only, never in the app
